_sText:
Hey guys!
This is my second map, Jb_paper_alive.

This is smaller than my first but is also very well;)

It contains:
-The game-planes (you have to dodge them)

-The game of "Left Right", it looks like a football field and CTs have to kill the last terrorist to get on the side designed by the screen (if a Trollface appears, it means move other side ^ ^)
-A small race with platforms 
-A Team game (texture of this game in french sorry, you'll have to figure that represents the picture but it's not very complicated) You make two teams, and each must make the shape shown on the screen, cts denote the fastest;)

-A relaxation room with a pool, a whirlpool, music, and a FreeStyleRoom; D

-The game of light sabers .... this game has caused me many problems and many bug, there is still a bug: never look at the ceiling when you have a sword. If you find other bug call me :)

One thing that will be useful: "Reservoir a terroriste" means the places where you can place the terrorists

I leave you with the beginning of my next map Jb_bisounours_party; D
